DAY 8 OF 90 DAYS OF DEVOPS
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
** GIT --- Version Control System that allows us to track changes to the file and co-ordinate work on those files among multiple people. Used to track changes to any set 
of files.
..................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................
** GITHUB -- Platform for developers to share and collaborate projects and used for hosting open source projects.
..................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................
** Version Control System and its Types --
System thet tracks changes to the files and allows us to revert back to previous state and compare changes over time.
* Types:
1. Distributed VCS - allows developers to clone an entire repository including the entire version history of the project
2. Centralized VCS - uses a central server to store all the versions of a project's files
......................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................
** Distributed VCS over Centralized VCS
1. Better Collaboration
2. Improve speed
3. Greater Flexibilty
4. Enhanced security
..................................................................................................................................................................................
TASK 1- Create a new repository on GitHub and clone it to your local machine
->> git clone https://github.com/muskanbhutani08/90DaysChallengeSoln.git
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
TASK 2-Make some changes to a file in the repository and commit them to the repository using Git
->> vim commands.txt
git add commands.txt
git commit -m "clonning file"
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
TASK 3- Push the changes back to the repository on GitHub
-->> git push origin main
